java.lang.Object
  alphabetsoup.framework.QuadtreeNode

public class QuadtreeNode
extends java.lang.Object

QuadtreeNode is the class that makes up the nodes of the Quadtree and performs recursive functions.

x1_pos - x coordinate of the top left corner of the bounding area.

x2_pos - x coordinate of the bottom right corner of the bounding area.
y2_pos - y coordinate of the bottom right corner of the bounding area.
